                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Olney</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">MacVeagh</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-12-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 26, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 219.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: The Department has been gratified to learn from
                    your No. 220, of the 11th instant, of the discharge of Vittorio Gardella, a
                    naturalized American citizen of Italian origin, from the military service of
                    Italy by a grant of unlimited leave.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Richard Olney.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
